plot: An old urban legend from within Portland sewers comes to light when a murder is committed by an vicious, alligator-like wesen.

As a deadly crime spree begins to surface, a century-old urban legend takes shape in Portland's sewers and becomes Nick's latest case. In Europe, Adalind meets Prince Viktor, who comes to bring those responsible for his cousin Eric's demise to justice. Meanwhile, Captain Renard responds to the recent attempt on his life.—Norby
